snippet.title: STEIN.WORLD - Official Alpha Trailer 2018
snippet.description:
FREE TO PLAY: https://stein.world/
The official gameplay trailer for stein.world 
Stein is a free to play massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) for your browser. Start playing today and join thousands of other players in the beautiful fantasy world of stein.

Website: https://stein.world/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/steingame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/pg5_studio
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/stein_world/
itch.io: https://pg5-studio.itch.io/steinworld
